@startuml aurelien-m_raspberrypi-rustpy

actor User
participant "Web Browser" as Browser
participant "Rust Web Server" as WebServer
participant "Python Controller" as PythonController
participant "Rust Library" as RustLib
participant "Raspberry Pi Hardware" as Hardware

User -> Browser: Access web interface
Browser -> WebServer: HTTP request
WebServer -> WebServer: Authenticate user
WebServer --> Browser: Serve HTML/JS/CSS

Browser -> WebServer: WebSocket connection
WebServer -> PythonController: ZeroMQ connection

User -> Browser: Select LED mode/settings
Browser -> WebServer: Send control commands
WebServer -> PythonController: Forward commands

PythonController -> RustLib: Call hardware functions
RustLib -> Hardware: Control LEDs

Hardware --> RustLib: Hardware state
RustLib --> PythonController: Update state
PythonController --> WebServer: Send updates
WebServer --> Browser: Real-time updates via WebSocket

PythonController -> PythonController: Process data (e.g., cosmic radiation)

Browser -> WebServer: Request system info
WebServer -> Hardware: Get CPU temperature
Hardware --> WebServer: Return CPU temp
WebServer --> Browser: Display system info

@enduml